{"tid":996144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全球爆流感　日本達警報級","createTime":"2019-01-26T05:02:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T05:18:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9b632307fab145cefdec4286d7d9d509b20f1052","tid":996144,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T05:02:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190126/20599330\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190126%2F20599330&d=5LGFuo5nUsA%2Bmel9t3wDT57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=b2a68ccd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190126%2F20599330&h=2cbaf66a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190126/20599330</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月26日 <br />\n<br />\n全球爆流感　日本達警報級<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190126/large/26la8p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190126%2Flarge%2F26la8p1.jpg&h=abed9456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幼稚園在農曆新年假前最後一天上學，有職員為學童探熱。謝榮耀攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】近日流感肆虐，連港人最愛的旅遊熱點日本也無法倖免。衞生防護中心提醒市民，農曆新年假期外遊時，應留意旅遊相關傳染病。日本的流感活躍程度已升至甚高水平，當地監測顯示流感疾病個案平均數目，由一月份首周的16.30，急升逾一倍至第二周的38.54。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：公院醫生怒轟「等到失救先叫爆煲？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190126/large/a0802a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190126%2Flarge%2Fa0802a.gif&h=6bb57a48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰國墨西哥登革熱流行<br />\n<br />\n港人旅遊熱點台灣、韓國及日本均爆發流感，美加及歐洲亦流行甲型H1病毒，其中日本流感患者人數正急增，已達到「警報層級」，顯示流感大規模流行。東京一名上班族女性患上流感懷疑因為身體不適，在地鐵站月台跌落路軌身亡。一間安老院更有七名院友集體感染流感死亡。<br />\n<br />\n另外，登革熱一直在部份亞洲地區流行。據今年最新數字，泰國、新加坡（自去年12月30日起）和日本已分別錄得1,679宗、822宗及15宗個案；在美洲，墨西哥今年錄得1,599宗個案。要預防蚊傳疾病，市民外遊時應穿寬鬆及淺色長袖上衣及長褲，並為外露皮膚塗上驅蚊劑。中國內地則自去年8月至今，分別錄得8宗人類感染禽流感（H5N6及H9N2）個案，當中一半位於廣東。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳沛冰  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n何栢良引述兒科醫護「病房如戰地醫院」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n公院醫生怒轟「等到失救先叫爆煲？」"},{"pid":"36b703828e16628d1ec71d0197cad2ac5b23345c","tid":996144,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T05:06:39.000Z","msg":"🇯🇵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2152d41106674575734033d529b9b7c6b5a5ce7","tid":996144,"uid":183219,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T05:14:42.000Z","msg":"支那又害人"},{"pid":"524d8573a9ee8503fee43addccd537505f9be181","tid":996144,"uid":224452,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T05:16:31.000Z","msg":"🇯🇵 天日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c207505f293bf21fdafa5c60533b65262c6730","tid":996144,"uid":38109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T05:16:54.000Z","msg":"咁打流感針黎做乜"},{"pid":"253cf0e2a1ed3fee4eb84454510908dac4159086","tid":996144,"uid":52911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8c207505f293bf21fdafa5c60533b65262c6730","tid":996144,"uid":38109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T05:16:54.000Z","msg":"咁打流感針黎做乜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T05:17:59.000Z","msg":"希望你唔係真係護士"},{"pid":"e94e6624efadc2bb72b5f2be46b3d35ddbe36f8c","tid":996144,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"253cf0e2a1ed3fee4eb84454510908dac4159086","tid":996144,"uid":52911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8c207505f293bf21fdafa5c60533b65262c6730","tid":996144,"uid":38109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T05:16:54.000Z","msg":"咁打流感針黎做乜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T05:17:59.000Z","msg":"希望你唔係真係護士"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T05:18:39.000Z","msg":"今年中唔中丫d antigen"},{"pid":"1a267949967f92dfd1700aa46310ca5be8e6b2d6","tid":996144,"uid":131441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T05:18:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}